default can be interpreted using a
defaultny of a number 
defaultof tools for statutor
defaulty interpretation 
defaultcurrently 
defaultavailable. 
defaultJ
defaultudges have not been required to give the Act any ‘higher’ status. It is true that, on occasions, very senior judges, especially in the House of Lords or Supreme Court, have treated the 1998 Act as if it were indeed a 
defaultconst
defaulti
